Workflow.Name: Review Hub - Delete Excel Files Older Than A Week
Workflow.Description:
This flow deletes all excel files that have been generated using the bulk update or create metric feature and have not been modified in over a week.
Flow failure results in the build-up of redundant excel files in the Review Hubs Sharepoint site.
